{"tid":162622,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇SLS巴打:p","createTime":"2017-03-19T12:03:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T09:56:07.000Z","uid":89282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3fe3d69d4d4fc4bddb0428fd72c43969a6e132d3","tid":162622,"uid":89282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T12:03:18.000Z","msg":"你地練聲練幾耐先由light mix練到balanced mix,再到full mixed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nrange extend個進度又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 仲係light mix撚 range D2-C5(計埋head同falsetto<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b72f423cd92a9199a1721f4e0a1c142bacde9a3","tid":162622,"uid":89282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T07:20:17.000Z","msg":"冇人學SLS?"},{"pid":"f20af358266ef2490d01e55ffa8305066b7b1b19","tid":162622,"uid":2852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T10:48:33.000Z","msg":"學左幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49171462c64588568596733b8fb0df9e36f31b39","tid":162622,"uid":89282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T13:25:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學左幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一年都未夠"},{"pid":"e515992e7882d45f9d77c8f4f1519f7a9a20401b","tid":162622,"uid":2852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T15:10:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>學左幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一年都未夠</blockquote><br />\n同你差唔多情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59292f79c9e3005e0b2608abbe8e4857bfdf76b5","tid":162622,"uid":77052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T18:38:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你地練聲練幾耐先由light mix練到balanced mix,再到full mixed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nrange extend個進度又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 仲係light mix撚 range D2-C5(計埋head同falsetto<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試下將軟腭向上扯，加埋主動去增強小小聲帶閉合（用腹式呼吸帶動），應該進步會快好多<br />\n其實C5差唔多到head個位架啦，所以你唱唔上去十有八九係未清楚發聲肌肉正確嘅動作同協調<br />\n而falsetto同head其實根本就係一樣嘢，只係個聲帶閉合嘅程度唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望你早日成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b44cc90bb894998bf77cae0d3606e0e3fb9bc049","tid":162622,"uid":89282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T05:18:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你地練聲練幾耐先由light mix練到balanced mix,再到full mixed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nrange extend個進度又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 仲係light mix撚 range D2-C5(計埋head同falsetto<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試下將軟腭向上扯，加埋主動去增強小小聲帶閉合（用腹式呼吸帶動），應該進步會快好多<br />\n其實C5差唔多到head個位架啦，所以你唱唔上去十有八九係未清楚發聲肌肉正確嘅動作同協調<br />\n而falsetto同head其實根本就係一樣嘢，只係個聲帶閉合嘅程度唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望你早日成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n發覺堆高音似head多過似mix係咩情況，E4-B4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56ceb2d5a809ad1397c382ad626af70426ed4a0","tid":162622,"uid":77052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T09:56:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你地練聲練幾耐先由light mix練到balanced mix,再到full mixed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nrange extend個進度又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 仲係light mix撚 range D2-C5(計埋head同falsetto<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試下將軟腭向上扯，加埋主動去增強小小聲帶閉合（用腹式呼吸帶動），應該進步會快好多<br />\n其實C5差唔多到head個位架啦，所以你唱唔上去十有八九係未清楚發聲肌肉正確嘅動作同協調<br />\n而falsetto同head其實根本就係一樣嘢，只係個聲帶閉合嘅程度唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望你早日成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n發覺堆高音似head多過似mix係咩情況，E4-B4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實有一D派別會用音高嚟直接定義head mix 同chest<br />\n妳講嘅E4到B4其實算係mix嘅音域範圍入面<br />\n但係我唔確定妳所講嘅似head到底係咩聲，所以我無辦法去準確咁判斷，但係可能性有以下兩個：<br />\n1.係舌頭不自主內縮，舌根下壓，造成喉部空間擴大，令音色變得唔明亮，渾厚，無mix果種有小小金屬感般明亮嘅音色<br />\n2.就係聲帶閉合做唔夠，導致比較多氣息出嚟，減少明亮嘅感覺（呢一點係因為聲帶閉合唔夠強嘅時候，咽壁管道嘅空間唔夠細，而明亮嘅感覺其實係靠細小嘅咽喉管去營造，好似吹口哨咁）"}]}